f allocating to this asset class in short the answer is potentially better riskadjusted returns since  investors in a basket of precious metals have benefited from relatively higher returns with lower risk thanks to the low correlation to equities and fixed income that precious metals often exhibit in many circumstances precious metals may provide a diversification benefit helping to offset swings in equities and fixed income indeed during severe market corrections precious metals tend to perform positively in some cases functioning as a hedge and providing some measure of protection during selloffs at etf securities we offer a broad suite of physicallybacked precious metals exchange traded funds etfs to help investors reach their investment goals in certain environments our commodities focused offerings below may provide diversification benefits in an effort to boost riskadjusted returns download brochure resource center click the icons below to view the documents metal product video primer factsheet prospectus gold etf securities physical swiss gold shares sgol silver etf securities physical silver shares sivr platinum etf securities physical platinum shares pplt palladium etf securities physical palladium shares pall metals basket etf securities physical precious metals basket gltr   gold  etf securities physical swiss gold shares sgol video primer factsheet prospectus  silver  etf securities physical silver shares sivr video primer factsheet prospectus  platinum  etf securities physical platinum shares pplt video primer factsheet prospectus  palladium  etf securities physical palladium shares pall video primer factsheet prospectus  metals basket  etf securities physical precious metals basket gltr video primer factsheet prospectus  contact us for additional information on our products and educational resources about us globally etf securities provides accessible investment solutions enabling investors to intelligently diversify their portfolios beyond traditiona